comments.content:
There's nothing here but a command and its output.  There really needs to be a clear description of the bug if you think there is one.

In this case, my guess is that you're showing that the instance could not connect to the metadata server.  I'm going to convert this bug into a question, which is the more appropriate place to get help figuring out what is going on with your setup.
